name: Yellow Slider
description:
Sub-title: “Lovecraftian Floral Horror 003”

Third in My ongoing series of cosmic horror floral nightmares. This piece was created with yellow roses and Japanese magnolia blossoms. The eyes and colours remind Me of yellow slider turtles.

Two artificial intelligence systems (VQGAN+CLIP) created this work. No input image was used.

2752x2752 pixel PNG

Minted December 11th, 2021. Verify via Twitter account @tormential and/or Instagram account @_tormential_ and/or vqgan.tormential.tez
